name: JayTech Techno
overview:
Since our Establishment in year 2005, we, “Jay Tech Techno Services” is a renowned organization involved in manufacturing and supplying a commendable range of Plastic Mold, Investment Casting, Cutting Die & Emboss Die, Investment Casting Die, Aluminium Pressure Casting Die, Die Pattern and Auto Forge.

Our Team: Backed by proficient and competent team of expert professionals, we have achieved milestones of success in short period of time. We have appointed our team after rigorous assessment of their skills on the basis of their qualifications and experience in this industry.

Our Infrastructure: We are blessed with the sophisticated infrastructure set-up at our premises, which enable us to manufacture Plastic Mold, Investment Casting, Cutting Die & Emboss Die, Investment Casting Die, Aluminium Pressure Casting Die, Die Pattern and Auto Forge.

Client satisfaction: In order to attain maximum satisfaction of our clients, we are engaged in manufacturing and supplying Plastic Mold, Investment Casting, Cutting Die & Emboss Die, Investment Casting Die, Aluminium Pressure Casting Die, Die Pattern and Auto Forge.

Why Us?: Unique assortment under a single roof Quality assured products Wide distribution network Ability to accept bulk orders Timely delivery of consignment Transparent business deals
